<body>
    <h1>Task 11 - Technical Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"288b82ffcb25" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-1.Intr=
oduction">1. Introduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"2eb8d91ed950" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-1.1Purpose">1.=
1 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"156f1ff148bb">The purpose of this document is to describe th=
e technical implementation of deploying the <strong>Bookstore API applicati=
on</strong> using a <strong>2-tier architecture on AWS</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c88f9e670c38">This document explains:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7b14a7e784ea">
<li local-id=3D"b54f3766c2a7">
<p local-id=3D"3e1b4b2fc303">Infrastructure setup</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ee8e8a957770">
<p local-id=3D"a1e2cee693cc">Application deployment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"542f14626cf6">
<p local-id=3D"dcac629e32f7">Database configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6c04d5a29981">
<p local-id=3D"c4ee7a211596">Security practices</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a48d38574097">
<p local-id=3D"52222749f11f">Monitoring setup</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"78446965b36c">The intended audience includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8706a6a75064">
<li local-id=3D"b75575bf1919">
<p local-id=3D"c0311b1b571d">CTO</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"843c1fdb4d9d">
<p local-id=3D"0104eca41206">Developers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7496e2e28212">
<p local-id=3D"353050b4c12c">Solution Architects</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"36b934813e94">
<p local-id=3D"206c31ecc9ea">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"78114f6e4009">
<p local-id=3D"c30f862d0cb8">Resellers and technical stakeholders.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"5d66095dc0b5">
<h2 local-id=3D"181e159a0c8d" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-1.2Scope">1.2 =
Scope</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8f71ca784a11">This document covers the deployment of the <st=
rong>Bookstore API application</strong> in a <strong>2-tier architecture</s=
trong>, separating the <strong>application layer</strong> and <strong>datab=
ase layer</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"76f90d7fcf1c">The scope includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b378813cca5b">
<li local-id=3D"57ff671fd786">
<p local-id=3D"63f8b435067e">Deploying FastAPI application on AWS EC2</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"31f7675c9aef">
<p local-id=3D"287b5fa8280d">Configuring MongoDB database using MongoDB Atl=
as</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"eca446815d7f">
<p local-id=3D"043b7d768721">Integrating the application with the database<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ae84885b1035">
<p local-id=3D"32cacd26092a">Implementing security group configurations</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"64ef26301593">
<p local-id=3D"87704de1fa7b">Basic monitoring and API verification</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"7511986ff81f">The scope <strong>does not include CI/CD pipel=
ine automation</strong>, infrastructure as code, or multi-environment deplo=
yments because they are outside the requirements of this task.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"aae86a9895f3">
<h1 local-id=3D"48218cbfef63" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-2.OverviewofDe=
vOpsProject">2. Overview of DevOps Project</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"44f49ab56add" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-2.1Definition"=
>2.1 Definition</h2>
<p local-id=3D"1bae3e7d95cf">This project demonstrates the deployment of a =
<strong>FastAPI-based Bookstore API</strong> using a <strong>2-tier archite=
cture</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"dd51baf7c06e">The architecture separates:</p>
<p local-id=3D"ee8ac09cefff"><strong>Application Layer</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ffb1598296c7">
<li local-id=3D"d7673c0e8364">
<p local-id=3D"b50bb3ec934c">FastAPI running on AWS EC2.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"68a393c926e0"><strong>Database Layer</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"f3b7c1934f1d">
<li local-id=3D"b73eb33b157e">
<p local-id=3D"e2b170179829">MongoDB database hosted on MongoDB Atlas.</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"dedd5885f821">This separation improves:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9ecc61a22396">
<li local-id=3D"381afa8afe59">
<p local-id=3D"ed4578c3e619">Security</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c7963e624d77">
<p local-id=3D"98f9b5534f05">Scalability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3ac67249e39d">
<p local-id=3D"14290d9f5ad6">Maintainability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dbc2eba1a218">
<p local-id=3D"c95001c815b4">Infrastructure management.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"69cd2de16755">
<h2 local-id=3D"8f9f9723bd1a" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-2.2KeyPrincipl=
es(AWSWell-ArchitectedFramework)">2.2 Key Principles (AWS Well-Architected =
Framework)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"4899b4a641e8">The solution aligns with the <strong>AWS Well-=
Architected Framework</strong>.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"1fa3f0d1d97a" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-OperationalExc=
ellence">Operational Excellence</h3>
<p local-id=3D"99e6578a6832">Deployment steps were documented and verified.=
<br>
Monitoring dashboards were created to observe API behavior.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"592a4d4a8065" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-Security">Secu=
rity</h3>
<p local-id=3D"8c785da9de8e">During development, database credentials were =
configured directly in the deployment setup for testing purposes. In produc=
tion environments, credentials should be stored using secure mechanisms suc=
h as environment variables or secrets management systems.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"2d05ec4d4d84" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-Reliability">R=
eliability</h3>
<p local-id=3D"00e897136cee">The API server and database were deployed as s=
eparate layers, ensuring that database issues do not directly affect applic=
ation infrastructure.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"edccc36fbb31" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-PerformanceEff=
iciency">Performance Efficiency</h3>
<p local-id=3D"215b5a3f0808">FastAPI was used due to its high performance a=
nd asynchronous capabilities.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"60cdc2b1bce8" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-CostOptimizati=
on">Cost Optimization</h3>
<p local-id=3D"6ed20ad5bfb3">Free-tier resources were used including:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"5863b1123c9a">
<li local-id=3D"b5cb49860d7c">
<p local-id=3D"a719aaafbfc9">EC2 t2.micro instance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a59fc3968ed5">
<p local-id=3D"1cc0262acc4f">MongoDB Atlas free cluster.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"2c993ef4d2fa" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-Sustainability=
">Sustainability</h3>
<p local-id=3D"a0b1204a52cb">Cloud resources were selected based on minimal=
 infrastructure requirements for development environments.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"a65b0dd72d08">
<h2 local-id=3D"a4b026a90f66" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-2.3GoalsandObj=
ectives">2.3 Goals and Objectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"45e625f77974">The main objectives of this implementation wer=
e:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c78cc5ef47a6">
<li local-id=3D"80485318c37c">
<p local-id=3D"d189471810ce">Deploy the Bookstore API application on AWS.</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c6573938d7f5">
<p local-id=3D"cb0446e009aa">Separate application and database layers.</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"a66a5c4cf533">
<p local-id=3D"f80b2efca5b8">Ensure secure connectivity between application=
 and database.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a57484f6ad9e">
<p local-id=3D"1c30765395fd">Verify that the API can read and write data to=
 the database.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2e7cdd9f8e59">
<p local-id=3D"05d6701a3a40">Enable monitoring to observe application behav=
ior.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d507bad5ea88">
<h2 local-id=3D"b1d16b1201f4" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-2.4Constraints=
andAssumptions">2.4 Constraints and Assumptions</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"e9ddb60ea1be" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-Constraints">C=
onstraints</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"8ce2653fc759">
<li local-id=3D"f04d28d2c946">
<p local-id=3D"394e53a1289c">Time constraint: task required completion with=
in <strong>3 hours</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"21ad9fca3497">
<p local-id=3D"1da7b310526f">Limited infrastructure resources</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aacba1bac7ca">
<p local-id=3D"97d7bfa723e2">No CI/CD automation required</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"2e2892460f83" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-Assumptions">A=
ssumptions</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"f85399164ebb">
<li local-id=3D"b9cdeae3fa39">
<p local-id=3D"07f9b26375f7">AWS account access is available</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"83074c8971db">
<p local-id=3D"b049749ce391">MongoDB Atlas cluster is accessible</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"544c426a0919">
<p local-id=3D"e15ca963c263">Internet access is available for EC2 instance<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"045535034d59">
<h1 local-id=3D"10205c1bf112" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-3.Architecture=
andInfrastructure">3. Architecture and Infrastructure</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"37f129682599" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-3.1Infrastruct=
ureOverview">3.1 Infrastructure Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"6b07b5656b93">The infrastructure follows a <strong>2-tier ar=
chitecture</strong>.</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper ima=
ge-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence=
-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260315-195546-20260322-123654.=
png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"a9de0853343f823ecbab7166ddc23c85=
2a85549d529d095a76ef06289d7c660f" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassia=
n.net/wiki/download/attachments/1847492621/image-20260315-195546-20260322-1=
23654.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1774183042601&amp;cacheVersion=
=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"1468" data-width=3D"3082" data-unresolved=
-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1885668079" data-linked-res=
ource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-re=
source-default-alias=3D"image-20260315-195546-20260322-123654.png" data-bas=
e-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-ty=
pe=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1847492621" data-link=
ed-resource-container-version=3D"3" data-media-id=3D"b2c50b8b-1fc0-4638-895=
4-3509bbd8a487" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"222"></span>
<h3 local-id=3D"5af48518697b" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-ApplicationLay=
er">Application Layer</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"a7ae750b49d1">
<li local-id=3D"b9008ce05cfd">
<p local-id=3D"c845d84839d7">AWS EC2 Instance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7426aaafcbb1">
<p local-id=3D"eb3c6ead3e9e">FastAPI application</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"019a4d2bf1c5">
<p local-id=3D"5d27cb4a7c09">Uvicorn ASGI server</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"26d99384e1c4" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-DatabaseLayer"=
>Database Layer</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"0bf0b2c4e762">
<li local-id=3D"61a126a0a2d5">
<p local-id=3D"918248071b2b">MongoDB Atlas cluster</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b574bf6188fc">The application communicates with MongoDB usin=
g the connection string stored in environment variables.</p>
<p local-id=3D"930623eb942c"></p>
<hr local-id=3D"1e743d5845c2">
<h2 local-id=3D"cdeb6e37d1a8" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-3.2Environment=
s">3.2 Environments</h2>
<p local-id=3D"f34acbc1263a">Only a <strong>single development environment<=
/strong> was used for this implementation.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"e=
7ee8e46-6a9a-4ed4-a559-33f5e1f4a67a" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"30e516c58008">
<th data-local-id=3D"5439674692e8" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"c01658a18279">Environment</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"d2d41ce50560" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"cdd6893e31d0">Purpose</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4036958a31a4">
<td data-local-id=3D"cdd0531b8979" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8ca4c8e4677d">Development</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3be13f66efaf" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"458733dad782">Used to deploy and test the Bookstore API</p><=
/td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"c8df6e0e90e0">Staging and production environments were <stro=
ng>not implemented in this task</strong>.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"a8282da37ca9">
<h2 local-id=3D"55a88e3752e6" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-3.3ToolsandTec=
hnologies">3.3 Tools and Technologies</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"4=
5774607-8113-49b1-b010-095bf75ed21b" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"a245b17a136d">
<th data-local-id=3D"af57bcd3a93a" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"6db100b9f324">Tool</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"3897a7c9d5c4" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"5c737b90459c">Purpose</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"15fed040f343">
<td data-local-id=3D"cba0a55bd8af" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"eab4ac47c05c">AWS EC2</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9ec78d304823" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0e792bae8ec4">Hosting the FastAPI application</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"0ec29c764f3d">
<td data-local-id=3D"06fad3b02d7a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"91335c8f6b6c">MongoDB Atlas</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"48f72a85963b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4e613ec3ba18">Managed database service</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"aaabe5b063d9">
<td data-local-id=3D"488cbaa59430" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9bc2e6e6b6b8">FastAPI</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4580174bd508" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"89e16e63f5be">Backend API framework</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"3b581f4a5a24">
<td data-local-id=3D"cd12c5a308c6" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1d85b3df0579">Python</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"29e67df1b200" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d8be46204e09">Application runtime</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"3207a13091f9">
<td data-local-id=3D"d7b8555cbf3c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8d0363da1e6d">GitHub</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ec6814e0c965" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b4a37285a4db">Source code repository</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"dd45eecb812a">
<td data-local-id=3D"d25d0d845543" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e975f7e220e1">Uvicorn</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"041afa8993fc" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7b02fc0b876d">ASGI server for FastAPI</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"814d47f04a51">
<td data-local-id=3D"8ae33ad99f36" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c38505a07cfd">New Relic</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b0db1ba5bf99" class=3D"confluenceTd">
