<p local-id=3D"41fb7c7f1f59">Repository used:</p>
<p local-id=3D"1230944bb560"><a href=3D"https://github.com/pushkar-iamops/b=
ookstore-api" local-id=3D"b8c42148e9a9" data-card-appearance=3D"inline" cla=
ss=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://github.com/pushkar-iamops/boo=
kstore-api</a></p>
<hr local-id=3D"d27ca10f12e0">
<h2 local-id=3D"65544bac213b" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-3.4Application=
Architecture&amp;UserRequestFlow">3.4 Application Architecture &amp; User R=
equest Flow</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"45f95af3f388" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-Architecture">=
Architecture</h3>
<p local-id=3D"c54ccd08b22b">User =E2=86=92 FastAPI (EC2) =E2=86=92 MongoDB=
 Atlas</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"52cb90c691ff" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-RequestFlow">R=
equest Flow</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"91a3b97ad0f8">
<li local-id=3D"c24de04a92e1">
<p local-id=3D"4fb374ba6808">User sends an API request.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"56b4bc289911">
<p local-id=3D"24695e434e8c">The request reaches the FastAPI application ru=
nning on EC2.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1a682420c657">
<p local-id=3D"636dc1e667e2">FastAPI processes the request.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6d6e0db2bfad">
<p local-id=3D"514f9be7771c">If data access is required, the application qu=
eries MongoDB Atlas.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b977c7174545">
<p local-id=3D"50b4fbe8af97">MongoDB returns the requested data.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b8f81d2d42b7">
<p local-id=3D"3d3003d5c041">FastAPI sends the response back to the user.</=
p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"cdbffac6be48">This ensures a clear separation between applic=
ation logic and database storage.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"3da51fe0d228">
<h1 local-id=3D"32622e665b17" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-4.DevelopmentP=
ractices">4. Development Practices</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"c050fe363175" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-4.1VersionCont=
rol">4.1 Version Control</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8a9b112a8443">The source code is maintained in a <strong>Git=
Hub repository</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"efb02f2d047a">Version control practices include:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8f2a932b10f8">
<li local-id=3D"9a3fdfbbbf2d">
<p local-id=3D"8084e31ea6dc">Cloning repository to EC2</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"98f89580dfbb">
<p local-id=3D"6cfb248500ff">Maintaining code versions through commits.</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"5eca0bb6341c">
<h2 local-id=3D"f7ba84625bad" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-4.2ContinuousI=
ntegration">4.2 Continuous Integration</h2>
<p local-id=3D"009500e06075">Continuous Integration (CI) pipelines were <st=
rong>not implemented</strong> as part of this task.</p>
<p local-id=3D"baab50df4f59">Deployment was performed manually on the EC2 i=
nstance.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"a514ef442566">
<h2 local-id=3D"daccd403dc1e" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-4.3AutomatedTe=
sting">4.3 Automated Testing</h2>
<p local-id=3D"303d42b67cf9">Automated testing tools were <strong>not imple=
mented</strong> for this project.</p>
<p local-id=3D"57ea18bc75e6">Instead, basic functional testing was performe=
d using:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"2109f5714112">
<li local-id=3D"a9a567697fd7">
<p local-id=3D"dd285ff8a320">FastAPI Swagger interface</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8f046c32e8d5">
<p local-id=3D"e84544839125">Direct API requests.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"c17fbd97a955">
<h2 local-id=3D"27215de7edef" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-4.4CodeQuality=
andAnalysis">4.4 Code Quality and Analysis</h2>
<p local-id=3D"3d81a5e3e39d">Formal code analysis tools were <strong>not us=
ed in this implementation</strong>.<br>
The project relies on standard Python coding practices.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"84af608b1160">
<h1 local-id=3D"8edd947962e4" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-5.Deploymentan=
dReleaseManagement">5. Deployment and Release Management</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"1baaa5285548" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-5.1DeploymentS=
trategy">5.1 Deployment Strategy</h2>
<p local-id=3D"972c8894b158">The application was deployed using a <strong>m=
anual deployment approach</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"7ba8719cc3fe">Deployment steps included:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"c90eec88b527">
<li local-id=3D"d5bc10158222">
<p local-id=3D"5755894f90e3">Launch EC2 instance.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1e8be6f52a2a">
<p local-id=3D"3739aa36d3b7">Install Python and required packages.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fdeb7cb46674">
<p local-id=3D"30e2bf76a07b">Clone repository from GitHub.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0a0f75b83f37">
<p local-id=3D"4613d49a7e60">Install application dependencies.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1fac14bd3d20">
<p local-id=3D"ab3ebc55f4e0">Run the FastAPI application using Uvicorn.</p>=
</li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"05c0bd3f16db">
<h2 local-id=3D"114b3a03d1ff" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-5.2Configurati=
onManagement">5.2 Configuration Management</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b37fc24a72f3">For this implementation, configuration values =
such as the MongoDB connection string were <strong>directly configured with=
in the deployment script for testing purposes</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"4d2571b0a7fc">This approach was used to simplify the deploym=
ent process during the development and testing phase of the project.</p>
<p local-id=3D"0dd8f0d1dd8a">In production environments, sensitive configur=
ation values should be stored using secure mechanisms such as:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"64baa386e959">
<li local-id=3D"9460a8a63de8">
<p local-id=3D"cd4739b379a5">Environment variables</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"95de225b69b5">
<p local-id=3D"819010758b02">AWS Secrets Manager</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b1fb3d3f75ec">
<p local-id=3D"f02fef1e0001">AWS Systems Manager Parameter Store</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f1081de371cc">This ensures credentials are not exposed withi=
n source code or deployment scripts.</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"0ebd293b4cf3" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-5.3ContinuousD=
elivery/Deployment">5.3 Continuous Delivery / Deployment</h2>
<p local-id=3D"512b0565653c">Continuous Delivery and Continuous Deployment =
pipelines were <strong>not implemented as part of this task</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"6cddcc8828e2">The application was deployed manually on the E=
C2 instance for development and testing purposes.</p>
<p local-id=3D"da63adc71a5e">Future improvements may include implementing C=
I/CD pipelines using tools such as:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ec153a0fc966">
<li local-id=3D"5865bfca62e6">
<p local-id=3D"5bb43ad265d1">GitHub Actions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bddf77419489">
<p local-id=3D"ef57851bca99">Jenkins</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b1a20e4228fe">
<p local-id=3D"6347307349a4">AWS CodePipeline.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d3aff430f517">
<h1 local-id=3D"a704075a5819" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-6.Monitoringan=
dIncidentManagement">6. Monitoring and Incident Management</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"8007b3505d1e" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-6.1MonitoringT=
oolsandMetrics">6.1 Monitoring Tools and Metrics</h2>
<p local-id=3D"2661259d5e67">Monitoring was implemented using <strong>New R=
elic dashboards</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"6118736af260">Metrics monitored include:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"08120d417b88">
<li local-id=3D"6467c563aadd">
<p local-id=3D"a3620b6ceb2a">Total API requests</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c36e7ab05089">
<p local-id=3D"f631eac6e6ce">Error rate</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8b0fae186ac6">
<p local-id=3D"20eb7831724b">HTTP response status trends</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8f2e02a65999">
<p local-id=3D"c2e8c55fb0ca">API response time.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"640eb0205abc">
<h2 local-id=3D"eebad140c04a" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-6.2Alertingand=
Notification">6.2 Alerting and Notification</h2>
<p local-id=3D"18e8d258c547">Alerting mechanisms were <strong>not configure=
d in this implementation</strong> as the focus of this task was limited to =
deploying the application and validating application=E2=80=93database conne=
ctivity.</p>
<p local-id=3D"e84784b5c8f1">Monitoring dashboards were created to observe =
application behavior and API activity.</p>
<p local-id=3D"dd085274822e">In a production environment, alerting would ty=
pically be configured to detect:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"60f8cad80251">
<li local-id=3D"186e91ecb1cd">
<p local-id=3D"bca6ed86dc2d">High server error rates (5xx responses)</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"4473a89d564c">
<p local-id=3D"52866b101bdb">Increased client errors (4xx responses)</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"85ad02bd1370">
<p local-id=3D"fafbea1368d8">API availability issues</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b4b002859ac9">These alerts can be implemented using monitori=
ng tools such as <strong>New Relic Alerts or AWS CloudWatch Alarms</strong>=
.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"1a8187bcab46">
<h2 local-id=3D"728ffd50d976" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-6.3IncidentMan=
agement">6.3 Incident Management</h2>
<p local-id=3D"e261c3a80eca">If an incident occurs:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"5cae409b2c14">
<li local-id=3D"929344beb4ef">
<p local-id=3D"9b6e2ee4326e">Monitoring dashboards highlight abnormal metri=
cs.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"afc1f3ae57f1">
<p local-id=3D"ff9d200fde2d">Alerts notify the team.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"880653a079d6">
<p local-id=3D"c89b1074fe7e">Logs are analyzed to identify root cause.</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"29c1a45f5c42">
<p local-id=3D"5e085ffbb067">Service is restored by restarting the API or f=
ixing configuration.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"c849f9966480">
<h2 local-id=3D"ae8c6c107d37" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-7.Security&amp=
;Compliance">7. Security &amp; Compliance</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a287c5449daa">Basic security considerations were implemented=
 for this project.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d4d538bd84b8">The database was hosted separately from the ap=
plication server using MongoDB Atlas.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5203f85c62c7">Security groups were configured to control inb=
ound traffic to the EC2 instance.</p>
<p local-id=3D"b9f1faac63b3">For simplicity during development, the MongoDB=
 connection string was configured directly in the deployment setup.<br>
However, in production systems credentials should be securely managed using=
 services such as <strong>AWS Secrets Manager or environment variables</str=
ong>.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"0c8da1d4ff23">
<h1 local-id=3D"0cc181a69eb4" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-8.CostOptimiza=
tion">8. Cost Optimization</h1>
<p local-id=3D"8213ce7727e5">Cost optimization was achieved by:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"afc282e7f513">
<li local-id=3D"fe53b48e39f1">
<p local-id=3D"3b1f56dcd4f2">Using AWS Free Tier EC2 instance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d5f09975ae64">
<p local-id=3D"4565b617defb">Using MongoDB Atlas free cluster</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"69a839bc3d57">
<p local-id=3D"c25c488ef778">Limiting infrastructure components to necessar=
y services only.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"3944ac0d5050">These decisions reduce operational costs while=
 maintaining functional infrastructure.</p>
