<p local-id=3D"ac47710408d0"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
This screenshot shows the <strong>New Relic monitoring dashboard</strong> u=
sed to observe the behavior and performance of the deployed Bookstore API a=
pplication. The dashboard provides insights into application activity and p=
erformance metrics in real time.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ae44c2bd8d0c">The dashboard displays multiple monitoring pan=
els including:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"0dac9188db78">
<li local-id=3D"c340e829a396">
<p local-id=3D"b8d9c55b8405">Total API request count</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0007df77f486">
<p local-id=3D"1dc19c0bb103">Requests handled by each EC2 instance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0ff6193d2c7e">
<p local-id=3D"b7d067886ee9">Average API response time</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"00f43edc13d0">
<p local-id=3D"66dae7958ab6">Application error rate</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"bf8d855a10cd">These metrics help track application health, p=
erformance trends, and request distribution across the application servers.=
</p>
<p local-id=3D"52ca25d6458f"><strong>Purpose:</strong><br>
This artifact verifies that monitoring has been implemented for the deploye=
d application. The dashboard enables visibility into API usage patterns, in=
stance-level request distribution, and potential error trends.</p>
<h1 local-id=3D"69f3cbc57a10" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-10.Implementat=
ionTimeline">10. Implementation Timeline</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"5e805b467494" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-Phase1=E2=80=
=93InfrastructureSetup">Phase 1 =E2=80=93 Infrastructure Setup</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"bd013fe9b7ba">
<li local-id=3D"9a4178a33745">
<p local-id=3D"6f62be772fc7">Launch EC2 instance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d4f5416a7739">
<p local-id=3D"ecc014217beb">Configure security groups</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"71a1954386b4">
<p local-id=3D"cf8cd7b052fc">Install system dependencies.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"0acf8d718337">
<h2 local-id=3D"ee22e7b95058" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-Phase2=E2=80=
=93ApplicationDeployment">Phase 2 =E2=80=93 Application Deployment</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"6140b8b4f42d">
<li local-id=3D"4f89696b7541">
<p local-id=3D"37ea66e6c224">Clone repository</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"04b773807e37">
<p local-id=3D"94d6cb3b3784">Install Python dependencies</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0f9c734d61dd">
<p local-id=3D"3a4e7d2bd4e1">Run FastAPI application.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a9836a5ce0f1">
<h2 local-id=3D"560215cd6d91" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-Phase3=E2=80=
=93DatabaseIntegrationandTesting">Phase 3 =E2=80=93 Database Integration an=
d Testing</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"d459937a5538">
<li local-id=3D"b397e7b25f85">
<p local-id=3D"03b25244f9ae">Configure MongoDB Atlas cluster</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a7fa044a0220">
<p local-id=3D"d24e4c890475">Set environment variables</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"13b8e9b53193">
<p local-id=3D"3a727262fdf8">Test API endpoints.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e709ffe7bcda">
<h1 local-id=3D"d2b1a93df09c" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-11.ContinuousI=
mprovement">11. Continuous Improvement</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"9e5324d23793" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-11.1Feedbackan=
dRetrospectives">11.1 Feedback and Retrospectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"fd8bd768cebd">Future improvements may involve gathering feed=
back from developers and infrastructure teams.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"499cd72aced6">
<h2 local-id=3D"a972899cf976" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-11.2IterativeE=
nhancements">11.2 Iterative Enhancements</h2>
<p local-id=3D"dda583ba4521">Potential enhancements include:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"dd5b524c7a57">
<li local-id=3D"b8eb8c35335b">
<p local-id=3D"49941423673b">CI/CD pipeline implementation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c0cb290c5877">
<p local-id=3D"ed31f450eb4e">Infrastructure automation using Terraform</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"7f363e6dab4f">
<p local-id=3D"f4db87347a37">High availability architecture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"681e502f9614">
<p local-id=3D"780088f3fade">Advanced monitoring and alerting.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"8b4130ee13da">
<h1 local-id=3D"aa91059bf682" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-12.Conclusion"=
>12. Conclusion</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"5c0d5f9b93a3" id=3D"Task11-TechnicalDocument-12.1Summary">1=
2.1 Summary</h2>
<p local-id=3D"313abe0d6a5d">This project successfully deployed the <strong=
>Bookstore API using a 2-tier architecture on AWS</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"513460384ab4">The application runs on an EC2 instance while =
MongoDB Atlas provides the database layer.</p>
<p local-id=3D"20a91154d0a4">The architecture ensures separation of concern=
s, secure database access, and scalable infrastructure.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
